 In Orange Empire Conference women's tennis: 
</P>
<P>
 Fullerton 5, Golden West 4 -- Debby Springer and Laurie Smude held off Dana 
Ferdenand and Leia Ryan at No. 1 doubles, 7-6, 6-2, for host Fullerton (7-1, 
5-1). 
</P>
