 Brethren Christian 8, Covina Western Christian 7 -- Paul Stites singled in two 
runs in the bottom of the seventh to give Brethren Christian (1-3) the victory. 
Kurt Aguilar hit his second home run of the season in the first inning for the 
Warriors. 
