</P>
<P>
 L.A. Baptist 4, Calvary Chapel 1 -- Nate Laufer (2-0) struck out 13 and walked 
five to lead the Knights (4-1) to a first-round victory. 
</P>
<P>
 The senior right-hander helped his own cause in the fourth inning, driving in 
