of the season, striking out 11 and walking four. Keyna Bell had a two-run 
single in the the Coyotes' six-run third inning. Calabasas improved (3-1). 
</P>
<P>
 Krolik and catcher Jennifer Goodelinus each had two hits. 
</P>
<P>
