Coach KABC 22.3 4. 60 Minutes KCBS 20.2 5. Grace Under Fire KABC 19.5 6. Home 
Improvement (8 p.m.) KABC 19.1 7. Seinfeld KNBC 18.7 8. Turning Point KABC 17.7 
9. The Simpsons KTTV 16.8 10. Blossom KNBC 16.7 Weekly Averages 
