<P>
BRAXTON WINS TOP SOUL TRAIN AWARDS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Pop-soul balladeer Toni Braxton was the big winner at the eighth-annual Soul 
Train Music Awards at the Shrine Auditorium on Tuesday night, claiming two 
trophies: best female album for "Toni Braxton" and best single for "Breathe 
Again." 
</P>
<P>
