Awards she won this year by taking song of the year honors for "I Will Always 
Love You" from "The Bodyguard" soundtrack. She also received the Sammy Davis 
Jr. Entertainer of the Year award. 
</P>
<P>
 Other winners: male album, Babyface's "For the Cool in You"; new artist, 
H-Town; jazz album, Kenny G's "Breathless"; group album, Silk's "Lose Control"; 
rap album, Onyx's "Bac . . . up" , and music video, Janet Jackson's "If." 
