<DOCNO> LA031694-0234 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 023325 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
March 16, 1994, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
