<HEADLINE>
<P>
CIRQUE SETS COSTA MESA DATES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Cirque du Soleil's 1994-95 touring production, "Alegria," brings the company 
back to Orange County beginning Jan. 21.The performances at the South Coast 
Plaza mall in Costa Mesa follow the troupe's engagement at the Santa Monica 
Pier starting Oct. 6. Tickets for both go on sale Sunday. 
</P>
<P>
 The show, which will premiere internationally April 21 in Montreal features 
trapeze acrobats and trampoline tumblers, as well as contortionists and clowns. 
</P>
<P>
 Ticket prices range from $13.50 to $39.50 from Ticketmaster outlets and are 
available by phone from Ticketmaster Phone Charge at (714) 740-2000, (213) 
480-3232 and through the Cirque du Soleil box office at (310) 458-7773. 
</P>
